  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-stellar\">single-use</span> geometric beacon that probes the surrounding area for near-space <span class=\"name name-special\">anomalies</span>. Such objects are highly unpredictable.<br><br>Select the Detector and use Begin Scan (<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>) to begin the location process.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种<span class=\"name name-stellar\">一次性</span>几何信标，可在周围地区探测近空<span class=\"name name-special\">异象</span>。该类物件极难预测。<br><br>选择探测器并使用以开始扫描（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）即可开始定位流程。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種<span class=\"name name-stellar\">單次使用</span>的幾何信標，探測周圍的區域，尋找附近太空中的<span class=\"name name-special\">異常</span>。這樣的物體變幻莫測。<br><br>選擇偵測器，再使用「開始掃描」（<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span>）功能，即可開始尋找。"
  },
